data.description: Exquisite Log Cabin Dream Home on 5 Serene Acres in Michigan City, Indiana. Escape to your own private retreat in this stunning log cabin nestled within woods overlooking your private stocked pond. Enjoy gorgeous sunsets, wildlife & take in Natures Beautiful 4 Seasons! This custom home offers the perfect blend of rustic charm, modern amenities, ample space, making this an unforgettable place you'll never want to leave. Property includes 4 Bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, & Walkout Basement & an Expansive 3,000 Sq. Ft! Newer Constructed 60X40 Pole Barn in 2018 with 3-Overhead Garage Doors for All Your Toys & includes a Separate 24X24 OfficeArea for the Ultimate Convenience! Inside you're greeted by the warm embrace of the log cabin's rich, natural woodwork. The open-concept living area features a cozy stone fireplace, perfect for winter evenings. The spacious kitchen boasts modern appliances and custom island. Plenty of Room Everyone inside or outside! Schedule your private tour right away!
